java.sql
类 Types

java.lang.Object
  java.sql.Types

public class Types
extends Object

A class which defines constants used to identify generic SQL types, also called JDBC types. The type constant values are equivalent to those defined by X/OPEN.

从以下版本开始：
Android 1.0
